{"type": "article", "id": 18726, "title": "玻璃瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-09T07:10:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150132GKOuf3VSo08CJmRW.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是法国艺术家 Hubert le Gall 为香槟酒商 Ruinart 创作的玻璃瓶，一共 12 个，代表一年中的 12 月。这些玻璃瓶都有雕塑感的形状，似乎是香槟上的气泡和洒开的水纹，有些穿插了木质结构，让它像一个植物。12个月一循环，也象征着季节的变化和生命的循环。Ruinart 每年都会邀请艺术家以酒庄为元素进行艺术创作，<a href=\"http://www.ruinart.com/fr-fr/hubertlegall\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150130p3K4xteOlcQDLMoh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150130W8Pr9tedETCxUK4D.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150131HtXemAVL3rIj0xiJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150131CuBIsEr38yvYpqgQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150131VyolTHknrgKi6zm4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}